question: Question: This character writes a poem with the same title as the novel in which he appears; the subtitle to this character's poem is "A Voyage to Maryland." For 10 points each: [10] Name this character and "Poet Laureate of Maryland" who unfortunately has to marry the syphilitic prostitute Joan Toast.
